high_descs: Turn around and face the couch, then make a right, walk straight and face the small table to your right.
Grab the car keys from the table.

Turn right and walk straight toward the blue chair, make a quick left before you reach the chair, walk straight toward the fireplace, make a quick right before you reach the fireplace to face the couch.
Place the car keys next to the box on the couch.
Turn right and walk toward the door then make a left to face the blue chair.
Pick up another pair of car keys from the table between the blue chair and couch.
Turn around, walk straight toward the fireplace, then turn right to face the couch.
Place the second pair of car keys on the couch next to where you placed the other keys.
anns.task_desc: Place two pairs of keys on the couch.

high_descs: Turn around and take a step forward, then turn right and walk over to the end of the coffee table.
Pick up the set of keys off of the coffee table.
Turn right and begin walking forward, the hang a left and walk towards the fire place, turn right and walk over to the black couch.
Put the keys on the seat of the couch in front of the cardboard box.
Turn right and begin walking across the room, then hang a left and walk up to the small table in between the couch and the chair.
Pick up the set of keys off of the small table.
Turn around and begin walking forward, then turn right and walk over to the black couch on your right.
Place the keys on the couch to the right of the keys that are already there.
anns.task_desc: Move two keys to a black couch.

high_descs: Turn to the left then turn to the right
Walk over to the coffee table
Pick the keys up from the coffee table
Walk over to the couch and set the keys down on the couch cushion
Walk to the end table
Pick the second set of keys up
Walk the over to the couch
Set the second set of keys down on the couch by the first set of keys

high_descs: Turn left, go to the left short side of the coffee table and face the coffee table.
Take the keys from the coffee table.
Turn right, go straight and to the left to the couch.
Put the keys in front of the box on the couch.
Turn right, go straight, turn left towards the side table to the right of the couch, go to the side table.
Take the keys from the side table.
Go back to the couch to the left and face the couch.
Put the keys to the right of the other keys on the couch.
Walk around to the side of the table with keys on it in the middle of the room.
pick up the keys on the table.
Walk around the table and then over to face the couch.
Place the keys in front of the box on the couch.
Walk to face the table on the right side of the couch.
pick up the keys on the table.
Walk back to face the couch to the left of the table the keys were on.
place the keys beside the other keys on the couch.
